Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.69,0:00:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连续打败悟空和比克的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的英雄弗罗斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可他的真面目是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.48,0:01:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己挑起战争并平息战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.52,0:01:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,廉价收购因战火而荒废的土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.56,0:01:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后通过二次开发和重建的特权，大赚一笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我发明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.90,0:02:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,商业模式喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊，他干的这些勾当和弗利萨差不多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯规！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手使用了武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他偷偷使用毒针的事被揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,违反了比赛规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.55,0:02:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特被判失去资格，但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你让我丢这么大的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要把你破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.73,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要破坏他，也不需要判他出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一个轮到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要亲手打倒这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说算我赢也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.88,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来还真是有自信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候可别后悔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的声音，听了真不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.63,0:03:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卑鄙的弗罗斯特，会受到报应吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.17,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「化愤怒为力量吧！贝吉塔的全力战斗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事吧？比克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心点，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疏忽大意还为时过早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.59,0:03:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为我不用卑鄙手段就什么也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以不把我放在眼里对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.97,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卑鄙的手段才是我最大的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.84,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是，换一个角度也可以这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我至今为止的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直把最大的武器隐藏起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这支毒针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会在和你的比赛中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫不犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫不留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好地使用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还打算用吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把神圣的规则当什么啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次真的要取消你资格喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听，外面的人这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用取消资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.30,0:04:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么能因为取消资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.07,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就轻易放过这个恶心的混帐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸好帅啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.97,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，非得在那里耍帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敢妨碍我的话，连你也揍飞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来是OK了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，仅限这场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.30,0:05:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使用武器和毒都不算犯规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.57,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，规定是不能杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果，是因意外事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.34,0:05:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对手不幸身亡的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么判决呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,违反规则和杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎来到我的领域！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，请好好欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲜血淋漓的表演时间开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.25,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这废物！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芭朵斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来修好它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心，我已经手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可和他不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会用卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.92,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胜者是，贝吉塔选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干得不错！贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厉害！太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人想让我也继续参加比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以在帮我检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.59,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空身上也有被弗罗斯特的毒针刺伤的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用说，肯定能回去比赛的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我就在莫纳卡之后上场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在贝吉塔之后！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莫纳卡绝对要压轴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为…为什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.23,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么一定要莫纳卡做压轴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这是当然的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.93,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟…最强的放最后气氛才会高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是贝吉塔或者我先赢了比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气氛还没高涨就没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是这样也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.28,0:08:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说，莫纳卡看上去还真有威严啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自从看了第一场比赛的龟派气功后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就一直昏迷了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.56,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事！没什么！什么都没发生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要把莫纳卡的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隐瞒到什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然是隐瞒到最后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了，绝对不能说出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个，比赛结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能和我比试一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许和他说话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说几句有什么关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他好像有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别碰他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛！好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.07,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然打我干嘛啊，比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.60,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聚精会神的莫纳卡是非常危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阻碍到他的人，不管敌友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都会一瞬间被消灭，变成灰烬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经有个星球就因为这样被毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不会吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.79,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我要这样提心吊胆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这叫自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，被听到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，和大家通知一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更改比赛规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.59,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在刚才，新的立体屏障建好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,选手要是碰到它，就算是在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.43,0:10:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也会被当作出界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再给我点时间的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能做个更完美的屏障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋！那种事怎样都无所谓了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等下，等下，等下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.55,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可没听说要改变规则！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.25,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可真抱歉啊，兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，刚刚的比赛中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这边的屏障不是被弄坏了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.36,0:10:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是再发生那种事，不就太危险了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用屏障把舞台覆盖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺便定了空中出界的规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许擅自做决定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啊！会场设置由我来负责的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还胡乱改动规则！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有可能会伤到观众啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.74,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类会变成怎样与我无关！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝不允许你跳过我，擅做决定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你几步，你别得寸进尺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用和平的方法解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.12,0:11:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们猜拳决定怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜拳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头，剪子，布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头，剪子，布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布布布布布…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.33,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们想要的东西，都已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赢了的话随你们拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，输掉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用我说你们也明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕的立方体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.88,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能得到那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管是破坏神还是银河巡逻队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都别想追踪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.39,0:13:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传说中的杀手，希特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.03,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是奉象帕之命来杀我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是我所毁灭的星球当中的幸存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重金请你来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟…发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.59,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.40,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个立方体已经说好是要给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像用不着我出马了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,手都麻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜拳没分出胜负啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没看到有什么骗人的机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.73,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且，选手本人也说没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然不知道你有什么企图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我绝不会败在无聊的圈套上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位久等了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，下一回合的比赛继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舞台都弄好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧，玛盖特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就不能安静点吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙该不会是机器人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.78,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,66950系银河的金属人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那边的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.89,0:15:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该也有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是有听过又好像没听过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我再多学习学习！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手的下一个对手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.11,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来自第六宇宙的袄汰·玛盖特选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大块头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战斗方式我一眼就看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如外表所见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是用力量来弥补速度不足的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是速度与力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就不行了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.08,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏掉了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是机器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受到如此强烈的连续打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然毫发无伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挺结实的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.83,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不仅是速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量也增强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来要避免近战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在找什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，到底是怎么了，玛盖特选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他停止动作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看着空中的贝吉塔选手纹丝不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心背后，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.45,0:18:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,碰到屏障的话，就算出界了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.82,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在空中也限制规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是因为这货不擅长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说，这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的最佳位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打算防御吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.59,0:19:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他口中有武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,犯规！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶…啊…那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶…刚刚得到消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛盖特选手吐出来的是熔岩口水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不算是武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熔岩口水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个怪物真够荒唐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕！快看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好！过于在意屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作施展不开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危险啊爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能增强力量的不只是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你见识一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.22,0:20:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人的压倒性力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有多少力量都给我使出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上吧！贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况不太乐观呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没注意到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.98,0:21:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？怎么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别了亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.44,0:21:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红的天空下的我和你　我站在你右边　而你待在我的左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.54,0:22:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我很喜欢你　这一生都不会忘记你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.04,0:22:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想说出口　又咽了回去　不如还是　把话埋在心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.42,0:22:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然两人被困在　一场滂沱落花雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.63,0:22:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簌簌的　谱成一首动人旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.72,0:22:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少把你的身影　从我的眼前隐去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.98,0:22:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.36,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.13,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.22,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.57,0:22:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变得越来越热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.34,0:22:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去身体快吃不消了
